ich reports some parallels with Attic ceramic: Graef, Langlotz 1933, p.128, no.1523, N 456; Milne 1936, fig. 34, no.14; F.Xanthos IV, p.174, nos. 400-401. The sign is very common in the Elymian corpus from Grotta Vanella (see records from \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020008\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020008\u003C/a> to \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic020035\" target=\"_blank\">ISic020035\u003C/a>).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Biondi 1992 117, no. 2, pl. III.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002322\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002322\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Agostiniani 2021 380 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002320\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002320\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Graef, Langlotz 1933 p.128, no.1523, N 456 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002563\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002563\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Milne 1936 fig. 34, no.14 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002564\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002564\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Metzger 1972 p.174, nos. 400-401 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001748\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001748\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1  22 9  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[225,228,231,234,237,239,242,245,248],{"id":226,"html":227},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"xly-Grek\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xly-Grek\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id